parameters: Alright, let's do our best today.

(I hope Amelia is okay. She doesn't seem any
different.)

(Amelia's smile really is the best. It instantly
lifts my spirits.)
Ah, could it be that you're tired from class?
Masamune-kun, you still have a long way to go.

There's no way that's true. The usual training is
much harder.
Then, I'm expecting you to shine today as well.

It seems like there are no monsters here. We
finally made it, it seems.
Ah, this is the Magic Research Club room.

It's too early to relax. The real challenge starts
now.

We need to find evidence of the summoning ritual
here.

Of course, there's also a possibility that it
doesn't exist.

(There were too many things happening before we
arrived, I couldn't help but feel relieved)

Who gave you permission to enter the Magic
Research Club?

It seems like there were signs of someone invading
the defense dungeon, but I never expected it to be
you guys.

It seems like the detection magic was somehow
deactivated without us noticing, but with all that
commotion, we would have noticed.

The person next to me is Jackson, the
representative of the Magic Research Club.

Thank you for introducing me. I wanted to see the
largest club, the Magic Research Club.
Despite that, you seemed to be acting all sneaky.

You're not just testing your skills, are you? What
do you want?
I just wanted to take a look inside.

It's an unreasonable request. Non-members are not
allowed to enter.
Even if it's the Student Council.

You must have something you really don't want to
be seen.
Can't you let me visit for just a little while?
No, we are currently preparing for a certain plan.
We're being more cautious than usual.

A plan... You're definitely scheming something,
aren't you?

I haven't done anything bad. It's just a surprise
plan.

You're planning to steal magic power from the
students... no, from the people in this academy,
aren't you?

There's no way that's true. We, Elena and the
others, are just...
Enough talk. Intruders don't need explanations.
I'll capture you and throw you into a cell.
There's a prison in the academy?

It's just a disciplinary cell. Behave like an
adult there until the plan is finished.
I'll let you out once it's over, so don't worry.

I don't know how much power you have, but even you
can't escape punishment.

You won't receive any punishment. A new world is
about to come.
Is she on par with Amelia...?
Actually... I might be a little overwhelmed...

If only I didn't do unnecessary things, I could
have had a fun school life.
